td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Articles 7, 8 and 47 of the Charter of Fundamental Rights of the European Union (‘the Charter’), of Article 1(1), of Article 7(e) and of Article 13(1)(e) and (f) of Directive 95/46/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 24 October 1995 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data and on the free movement of such data (
OJ 1995 L 281, p. 31
), and of Article 4(3) TEU and of Article 267 TFEU.

Those requirements also appear in the recommendations of the Court of Justice of the European Union to national courts and tribunals in relation to the initiation of preliminary ruling proceedings (
OJ 2016 C 439, p. 1
).
